---
import CMG5 from "../../assets/images/ColdMix/GallerySlider/CMG5.png";
---
<div class="w-full md:px-32 px-8 flex flex-col justify-center items-center font-bold">
    <div class="text-end w-1/2 mt-24 self-end">
        <h1 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl">COLD MIX ASPHALT PLANTS</h1><br>
        <div class="h-0.5 bg-blueMain w-full"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="mt-6">
        <p class="text-grisP text-base md:text-lg">
            Cold mix plants are specifically engineered to produce asphalt mixtures without the 
            need for high temperatures. Using a robust pugmill mixer, these plants blend various
            aggregates with asphalt emulsion, delivering a uniform and durable mix suitable for multiple 
            applications.
            <br><br>
            Equipped with precision dosing hoppers, they ensure accurate control over material
             proportions, resulting in consistent performance across every batch. Their ability 
             to work with different aggregate types makes them ideal for patching, road repairs, 
             and small-scale paving projects.
            <br><br>
            Designed for ease of use, quick setup, and minimal maintenance, cold mix plants are a 
            practical solution for contractors, municipalities, and remote job sites—offering 
            dependable asphalt production whenever and wherever it’s needed.
        </p>
    </div>
    <div class="w-full flex justify-center my-10 px-8 md:px-52">
        <img src={CMG5.src} alt="" class="">
    </div>
    <div class="w-full bg-grisT rounded-xl p-8 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2">
        <div class="w-full text-white flex flex-col gap-3 justify-center">
            <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl">Cold Mixing = Eco-Friendly Mix</h1>
            <div class="w-full h-0.5 bg-white"></div>
            <p class="text-base md:text-lg">
                Designed for ease of use, quick setup, and minimal maintenance, cold mix plants are a practical solution
                 for contractors, municipalities, and remote job sites—offering dependable asphalt production whenever and
                  wherever it’s needed.
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="w-full">
            <img src={CMG5.src} alt="">
        </div>
    </div>

</div>